author: kwall
msg: PROTON-254: Resolve C++ compliation issues of the swig generated code for the Java binding
* Use Swig's JCALL macros to invoke JNI functions in order that code compiles under C or C++
* Bracket JNIEXPORTed functions in ifdef'd extern "C" {...} in order to preserve symbol name (which is critical to JNI)
* Add casting to resolve compile issues under C++
